00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:30,079
According to the intelligence previously gathered by Comrade Fengye,

336
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,480
the Peace Conference

337
00:21:31,759 --> 00:21:33,279
It's not as simple as it seems.

338
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:36,559
What is really hidden behind it

339
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,880
between the Wang Jingwei government and the Japanese

