397
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,480
Ma Zi and the others aren't bullying you, are they?

398
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:07,920
No, no, not at all.

399
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,640
The guys are really nice to me.

400
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:10,680
Group Leader Yu,

401
00:24:10,680 --> 00:24:12,480
he may look a bit fierce,

402
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,440
and he speaks a bit harshly,

403
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,839
sometimes even gets physical,

404
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,799
but actually,

405
00:24:15,799 --> 00:24:17,119
he's very loyal.

406
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:19,079
Captain Bai seems sharp,

407
00:24:19,079 --> 00:24:20,359
but when it comes to the team's food, clothing, and needs,

408
00:24:20,359 --> 00:24:21,759
he never skimps on anything.

409
00:24:22,559 --> 00:24:24,519
Even though those two bicker and mess around,

410
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:25,839
I actually feel

411
00:24:25,839 --> 00:24:28,200
they must be really close in private.

412
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:34,200
You observe things quite carefully.

413
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,279
Good morning, Director Liang.

414
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,160
Good morning, Director.

415
00:25:05,759 --> 00:25:06,559
Boss.

416
00:25:08,279 --> 00:25:09,039
Boss.

417
00:25:09,039 --> 00:25:10,559
So cool.

418
00:25:10,759 --> 00:25:11,920
Now that's more like you.

419
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:13,720
When you first came back, I barely recognized you.

420
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,359
What are you drinking?

421
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:18,480
Soy milk.

422
00:25:18,759 --> 00:25:19,920
Did you put too much sugar in it?

423
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:20,960
Your mouth is so sweet.

424
00:25:21,319 --> 00:25:22,160
How about you—

425
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,359
I’ll go get you a cup.

426
00:25:23,359 --> 00:25:24,160
No need.

427
00:25:24,279 --> 00:25:25,079
I knew it.

428
00:25:25,079 --> 00:25:26,799
Boss doesn’t like your weird stuff.

429
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,640
Who would drink something so sickly sweet?

430
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,720
You have to add soy sauce to soy milk.

431
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:30,519
Otherwise, it has no soul.

432
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:31,160
You know that, right?

433
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,599
What do you mean, my weird stuff?

434
00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:34,359
I just like it sweet, so what?

435
00:25:34,559 --> 00:25:36,160
Who puts soy sauce in their drink in the morning?

436
00:25:36,160 --> 00:25:37,440
And look at your hair.

437
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,680
Looks like you smeared soy sauce on it.

438
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:40,440
Fine, you don’t believe me?

439
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:41,000
Alright, come on.

440
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,039
Let’s get a second opinion.

441
00:25:42,039 --> 00:25:42,799
How do you drink it?

442
00:25:42,799 --> 00:25:43,359
You tell us.

443
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,039
Enough.

444
00:25:44,039 --> 00:25:44,559
You—

445
00:25:44,759 --> 00:25:45,920
Don’t you two have anything better to do?

446
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:47,440
You’re so bored you’re arguing over nothing.

447
00:25:47,559 --> 00:25:48,839
You two are obviously close.

448
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,880
You can’t go a minute without bickering, can you?

449
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,240
Who’s close with him?

450
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,559
Who wants to hang out with you?

451
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,759
You two, come in.

452
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,880
