453
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:08,599
Yeah.

454
00:26:08,599 --> 00:26:09,599
They're really attentive.

455
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:12,480
Do you ever use your brain?

456
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:14,200
The Japanese came by once.

457
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:17,440
Now the General Affairs Office thinks I'm easy to push around, right?

458
00:26:19,799 --> 00:26:20,720
That's what it means.

459
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,000
Boss.

460
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,319
I, Scarface, only respect you.

461
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,400
If the General Affairs Office bullies you again,

462
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,519
I'll go make trouble for them.

463
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:27,720
Or just send them back.

464
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,400
Say we don't need more people here.

465
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,200
We don't take in useless people.

466
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,240
They can go wherever they want.

467
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:32,200
Forget it.

468
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:34,720
If we do that, the General Affairs Office will have

469
00:26:34,720 --> 00:26:36,480
an excuse to argue with me.

470
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,119
Lao Bai.

471
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:41,119
That's why I say you don't think.

472
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,160
If you had a brain,

473
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:43,799
