00:27:33,519 --> 00:27:34,799
Let Zhao Di stay.

501
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,519
Set up a workstation for him outside.

502
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:39,480
Put the other two in the team for fieldwork.

503
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,240
Yes.

