00:30:01,079 --> 00:30:01,880
Xiao Si

509
00:30:02,039 --> 00:30:02,799
Brother

510
00:30:03,359 --> 00:30:04,599
Turn back

511
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:25,720
Mr. Lu

512
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,119
Please have some tea

513
00:30:28,759 --> 00:30:29,759
In just a few days

