how wrong their choice was.

571
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,519
Before that,

572
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,799
I have a gift for Mr. Lu.

573
00:33:10,319 --> 00:33:12,480
This was custom-made specifically for Mr. Lu.

574
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:14,680
Mr. Mizuno, what do you mean by this?

575
00:33:16,079 --> 00:33:17,880
Are you mocking me, Mr. Lu?

576
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:21,640
Humiliation can become a driving force in life.

577
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:23,359
Mr. Lu, perhaps you could see it as

578
00:33:23,359 --> 00:33:24,559
a well-intentioned reminder.

579
00:33:24,559 --> 00:33:25,480
A constant reminder to yourself

580
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:27,039
of why you ended up in this situation,

581
00:33:27,319 --> 00:33:29,400
and how you can endure hardship to make a comeback.

582
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:31,079
To wash away your shame.

583
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:00,440
Come in.

584
00:34:05,359 --> 00:34:06,160
Chief.

585
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:08,239
How did the investigation on those two girls go?

586
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:09,960
We didn't find anything useful.

587
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:15,079
What did you say?

588
00:34:15,159 --> 00:34:17,119
I said we didn't find anything useful.

589
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:18,840
Then keep investigating.

590
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:20,800
Get to the bottom of it for me.

591
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,800
Where has Liang Shuo been these past few days?

592
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,440
Has he met with this woman?

593
00:34:24,559 --> 00:34:25,360
Yes.

594
00:34:43,119 --> 00:34:43,920
Stop the car.

595
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,079
The weather is nice today.

596
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,480
I'll walk over by myself.

597
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:50,719
You can head back first.

598
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:08,880
What are you doing here?

599
00:35:09,559 --> 00:35:10,719
I have something to say to you.

600
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,960
This isn't the place to talk.

601
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:14,760
Come with me.

602
00:35:21,519 --> 00:35:22,280
Come in.

603
00:35:29,559 --> 00:35:30,440
Are you okay?

604
00:35:31,079 --> 00:35:33,280
I heard you almost lost your life.

605
00:35:33,559 --> 00:35:34,719
I wrongly blamed you.

606
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,440
You still haven't told me

607
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,559
how you got involved with Xie Jun'an.

608
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:41,599
He's my uncle.

609
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,719
Sorry.

610
00:35:44,119 --> 00:35:45,800
I didn't know you were related to him.

611
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,920
No wonder you also have the surname Xie.

612
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,239
Have a seat.

613
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,119
But

614
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,079
My name isn't Xie Yuxin

615
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,039
My real name is Nian Ci

616
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:05,039
Xie Nian Ci

617
00:36:05,599 --> 00:36:06,559
I promise you

618
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:09,199
From now on, I won't hide anything from you

619
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,199
So the two of them couldn't persuade me

620
00:36:16,679 --> 00:36:18,360
So they sent you to convince me

621
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,039
But let me tell you

622
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,880
No matter who I was before

623
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:27,880
Or what I've done

624
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,639
From now on

625
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:32,440
I don't want any more involvement with the Bureau

626
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:34,840
I just want to live a good life

627
00:36:35,079 --> 00:36:36,079
Do you understand?

628
00:36:37,559 --> 00:36:39,119
But Old Xie won't give up until he gets what he wants

629
00:36:39,119 --> 00:36:40,559
He absolutely won't let you go

630
00:36:41,559 --> 00:36:42,960
Just give him the item

631
00:36:44,119 --> 00:36:45,639
Make a deal with him

632
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:46,840
Right

633
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:48,480
I'll go talk to him

634
00:36:48,559 --> 00:36:49,800
You make a deal with him

635
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,599
Give him the item

636
00:36:50,599 --> 00:36:51,440
So he'll let you go

637
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:53,519
Then find a chance to escape from No. 76

638
00:36:53,559 --> 00:36:54,519
And get out of Shanghai

639
00:36:57,239 --> 00:36:58,599
You don't have to look at me like that

640
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,559
If you don't want to give him the item, that's fine too

641
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,719
I'll figure something out myself

642
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:05,320
I'll go now

643
00:37:05,719 --> 00:37:06,760
Wait a moment

644
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:28,320
The thing he wants

645
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,320
If you're willing to trust me

646
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,400
No. 17, Pingjia Lane

647
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,400
A residential house

648
00:37:33,519 --> 00:37:34,800
There's a passage under the bed

649
00:37:35,119 --> 00:37:36,639
Because it's not under Yan Jiu's name

650
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,159
So the Japanese didn't find it

651
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:39,679
Got it

652
00:37:41,039 --> 00:37:42,559
Handing it over to you

653
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,840
I've done all I can

654
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,239
I know

655
00:37:48,519 --> 00:37:49,679
You don't owe him anything

656
00:37:49,719 --> 00:37:50,599
I'll see you off

657
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,559
Director Liang

658
00:37:59,519 --> 00:38:00,599
It's me, Chen Gengsheng

659
00:38:04,519 --> 00:38:05,320
Who is it?

660
00:38:06,039 --> 00:38:07,079
I know you're home

661
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,559
Open the door

662
00:38:14,679 --> 00:38:15,480
Draw the curtains

663
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,159
Get under the covers

664
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:17,119
Take off your clothes

665
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:18,960
What are you talking about?

666
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,440
He's right at the door now

667
00:38:20,599 --> 00:38:21,599
You can't escape either

668
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,880
Believe it or not

669
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,000
Go watch the back door

670
00:38:30,360 --> 00:38:31,480
Keep a close eye for me

671
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,920
Chief Chen

672
00:39:05,239 --> 00:39:06,239
What a rare visitor.

673
00:39:06,239 --> 00:39:08,119
I didn't see you at headquarters today.

674
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:10,480
Are you here to check if I'm still alive?

675
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,599
Director Liang, what are you saying?

676
00:39:15,159 --> 00:39:17,000
Should I invite you in to sit for a while?

677
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,639
I don't think we're that close yet

678
00:39:18,639 --> 00:39:20,239
to just drop by each other's place.

679
00:39:24,559 --> 00:39:26,239
After all, we are colleagues.

680
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,840
Given Director Liang's character,

681
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:29,599
and since I brought a small gift,

682
00:39:29,679 --> 00:39:31,840
it wouldn't be right not to invite me in.

683
00:39:36,800 --> 00:39:38,559
I brought you two boxes of Longjing tea

684
00:39:38,559 --> 00:39:39,559
and two bottles of whisky.

685
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:40,840
Black & White brand.

686
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:41,880
Where should I put them for you?

687
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,519
Just put them on the table.

688
00:39:44,199 --> 00:39:45,440
Or maybe in the study?

689
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,800
So it's convenient for you to use.

690
00:39:49,199 --> 00:39:50,400
Director Liang, now that you've recovered,

691
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:51,840
I didn't get a chance

692
00:39:52,119 --> 00:39:53,280
to come by and congratulate you.

693
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:56,360
And with the Yulongshan incident before,

694
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,480
I'm truly sorry.

695
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:02,280
So I thought I'd make it up to you all at once.

696
00:40:02,599 --> 00:40:04,199
Chief Chen, you're too polite.

697
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:05,360
Please, you should go.

698
00:40:05,519 --> 00:40:07,880
Director Liang is still holding a grudge.

699
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:10,000
I'm really sorry.

700
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:12,800
It's all because the Japanese were pressing us too hard.

701
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,199
Of course,

702
00:40:14,199 --> 00:40:15,639
it was also the Director's decision.

703
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,360
Otherwise, how would I have dared?

704
00:40:18,239 --> 00:40:19,280
Director Liang

705
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:21,159
This phonograph is quite nice.

706
00:40:26,079 --> 00:40:26,920
Where did you buy it?

707
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:31,800
Was it expensive?

708
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,239
Team Leader Chen,

709
00:40:34,039 --> 00:40:35,079
we've finished talking,

710
00:40:35,079 --> 00:40:36,159
and the gift has been given.

711
00:40:36,159 --> 00:40:37,159
Can I leave now?

712
00:40:37,159 --> 00:40:38,599
You're in such a hurry to kick me out.

713
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:42,239
Do you still have guests at home who haven't left?

714
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:46,239
Chen Gengsheng,

715
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:48,559
are you spying on me?

716
00:40:48,559 --> 00:40:49,840
Since we're all friends,

717
00:40:50,639 --> 00:40:52,519
let's have some tea together.

718
00:40:55,239 --> 00:40:56,280
Get out.

719
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:58,920
Sorry.

720
00:41:01,679 --> 00:41:04,199
So Team Leader Chen has this kind of hobby.

721
00:41:04,239 --> 00:41:06,199
I should call headquarters and ask

722
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:07,719
who exactly gave the order

723
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:09,719
to investigate right up to my bed.

724
00:41:09,719 --> 00:41:10,440
Director Liang,

725
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,000
sorry.

726
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,719
I—I was being reckless.

727
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,559
I'll leave right away.

728
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,920
Sorry, sorry.

729
00:41:32,079 --> 00:41:32,880
He's gone.

730
00:41:36,159 --> 00:41:36,840
How did it go?

731
00:41:36,840 --> 00:41:37,920
Did we fool him?

732
00:41:39,400 --> 00:41:40,199
Thank you.

733
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:42,119
It's a bit early to thank me now.

734
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,280
Wait until I give you your freedom back to thank me.

735
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:45,239
I'll go now.
